        "bridge_3_headline": "What is actually inside each product",
        "bridge_3_p1": "The comparison table tells one story. But numbers on a page do not show you what is actually going into your body every morning and every evening.",
        "bridge_3_p2": "Coastline is built around 13 specific compounds -- each selected because the clinical evidence was too strong to ignore. Not 75 ingredients sprinkled in at trace amounts. Thirteen. Every single one at the dose used in the studies that proved it works.",
        "bridge_3_p3": "Here is exactly what is in the formula, how it is organized, and why each ingredient made the cut.",
        "ingredients_headline": "13 ingredients. Every dose disclosed.",
        "ingredients_subheadline": "Three products. One system. Optimized for your circadian rhythm.",
        "bj_inulin_callout": "Coastline includes clinical-dose inulin at 4g -- the very prebiotic Bryan Johnson recommends -- as just one of 13 ingredients.",
        "bridge_4_headline": "Built by researchers, not marketers",
        "bridge_4_p1": "We did not design this formulation in isolation. Coastline was built alongside a team of researchers and clinicians with decades of combined experience in circadian biology, molecular medicine, and human performance.",
        "bridge_4_p2": "Their job was simple: review thousands of studies and identify the compounds with the strongest evidence for human longevity. Not trends. Not marketing-friendly superfoods. Just what actually works, at doses that actually matter. Here is what they have to say about the result.",
        "expert_label": "WHAT RESEARCHERS SAY",
        "expert_1_quote": "The 13 ingredients chosen for Coastline are the most scientifically supported, and clinically validated supplements yet to be discovered.",
        "expert_1_name": "Greg Potter, PhD, MSc",
        "expert_1_credential": "Sleep & Circadian Health",
        "expert_2_quote": "Coastline is what happens when you combine scientific rigor with real-world clinical understanding.",
        "expert_2_name": "Dr. Jacqueline Jacques, ND",
        "expert_2_credential": "Naturopathic Medicine",
