        "expert_4_quote": "A comprehensive, evidence-based approach to longevity that I recommend to my patients.",
        "expert_4_name": "Chris Pollock, MD",
        "expert_4_credential": "Internal Medicine",
        "bridge_5_headline": "What real customers are saying",
        "bridge_5_p1": "Expert validation matters. But at the end of the day, what matters most is whether real people notice a real difference. Not in a lab. In their actual lives -- their mornings, their workouts, their energy at 3 PM, their sleep.",
        "bridge_5_p2": "We asked Coastline customers to share their experience. Many of them came from AG1 or other supplements. Some are physicians. Some are athletes. Some are parents who just wanted to stop feeling exhausted. Here is what they said.",
        "reviews_counter": "REAL REVIEWS",
        "reviews_headline": "People who made the switch",
