        "review_1_name": "Michael R., 62 - Physician",
        "review_2_quote": "Quality you can feel. You can tell this was made by scientists, not a marketing team.",
        "review_2_name": "Edward Q., 49",
        "review_3_quote": "I used to spend over $200 a month on five different supplements and still was not sure I was covering everything. Coastline replaced all of them. One system, done.",
        "review_3_name": "Lisa T., 52",
        "review_4_quote": "I'm extremely careful about what I put in my body. Coastline checked every box for purity and data.",
        "review_4_name": "Rachel G., 48",
        "review_5_quote": "I love the convenience of having everything I need in one simple system. No more pill organizers.",
        "review_5_name": "James U., 44",
        "review_6_quote": "Finally, a longevity stack that does not require 15 different bottles. My morning brain fog is gone.",
        "review_6_name": "Robert K., 45",
        "review_7_quote": "Three weeks in and the mental sharpness is unmistakable. I'm writing better code, retaining more from meetings, and my afternoon crash is just gone.",
        "review_7_name": "Thomas H., 43",
        "review_8_quote": "I stopped needing my second coffee by week two. The energy is steady -- no spike, no crash. Just consistent output from 6 AM to 10 PM.",
        "review_8_name": "Derek W., 47",
        "review_9_quote": "As a busy mother and entrepreneur, mental clarity is my most valuable asset. Coastline cleared the afternoon fog that I thought was just a permanent part of my life.",
        "review_9_name": "Sophia R., Founder",
        "review_10_quote": "I ran every ingredient through PubMed before buying. Every single one checks out at clinical doses. That never happens with supplement companies.",
        "review_10_name": "Andrew P., 55",
        "review_11_quote": "I train six days a week and recovery used to be my biggest bottleneck. Since starting Coastline, I'm bouncing back faster and my endurance has noticeably improved.",
        "review_11_name": "Marcus D., 39",
        "review_12_quote": "My naturopath actually recommended Coastline after reviewing the ingredient list. That kind of third-party validation sealed the deal for me.",
        "review_12_name": "Catherine W., 58",
        "review_13_quote": "My husband and I both switched to Coastline. We cancelled six separate subscriptions between us. Simpler, cheaper, and we actually feel the difference.",
